====================================READ ME====================================

Chatbot is a bot who can give you the forecast of any city you want. Just ask!

1. Add your wit.ai      key in wit.key      file at the root of the repository
2. Add your forecast.io key in forecast.key file at the root of the repository
3. Run with:

$ make

====================================TESTING====================================

In general:

$ make test

To test using istanbul and flow:

$ istanbul cover _mocha -- -R spec
$ npm run-script flow

To check coding style:

$ semistandart

